# Half Adder

> [!word] Half Adder
> The [[61-Archive/20220318121832-half-adder|Half Adder]] is a [[61-Archive/20220318121802-combinational-logic|Combinational Logic]] circuit that adds the two bits **A** and **B**, it gives the **sum** and the **carry** bit as the outputs
